---
---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="container about-inner">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-index">01 /</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">About</h2>
      <span class="section-rule"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="about-content reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <div class="about-accent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>
          IT Engineer with a background in service and project management, aspiring to
          contribute organizational talents and proven expertise to leading companies in
          the luxury and tech sectors. Highly curious individual with a strong desire for
          continuous learning and professional growth in dynamic environments.
        </p>
        <p>
          Experienced in Agile methodologies, data analytics, and service delivery
          optimization — I believe the best solutions come from understanding both the
          data and the people behind it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .about-accent {
    width: 3px;
    min-height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--color-gold), var(--color-accent));
    border-radius: 3px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about {
      padding: 3.5rem 0;
    }

    .about-content {
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .about-text p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
